{"word":"ἄπεδος","slug":"ἄπεδος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄπεδος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>α</el> <a href='S:copulative'>copul.</a> , <a href='S:πέδον'><el>πέδον</el></a>\n<p/><i>even, level, flat</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: —<el>ἄπεδον, ου, τό</el>, <i>a plain, flat surface</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}